<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") -%>

<div class="row mt-5 mb-5 px-3">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
        <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 rounded-4 p-4 p-md-5">
            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4">Cancellation & Refund Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-muted small">Last updated: March 13, 2026</p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            
            <div class="legal-content fs-6 lh-lg">
                <div class="alert alert-warning border-0 rounded-4 p-4 mb-5">
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-exclamation fs-3"></i>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">Important Notice</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0">Please note that all bookings made through VistaGo are <span class="fw-bold text-danger">strictly non-refundable</span>. Once a payment is processed, no refunds will be issued under any circumstances.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">1. Cancellation Policy</h4>
                    <p>You may cancel your booking at any time through your dashboard. However, as per our policy, no refund will be provided for any cancelled bookings regardless of the time of cancellation.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">2. Refund Eligibility</h4>
                    <p>There is <span class="fw-bold">no refund</span> for any payments made. This includes partial payments, security deposits (if any), and full booking fees. By initiating a payment on VistaGo, you acknowledge and agree to this no-refund policy.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">3. Exceptions</h4>
                    <p>In extreme cases where a host cancels a booking or a property is unavailable due to VistaGo's error, we may offer a credit for future bookings at our sole discretion. This does not constitute a refund.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">4. Chargebacks</h4>
                    <p>Any attempt to initiate a chargeback with your bank for a valid VistaGo booking will be contested using these terms. We recommend contacting our support team before reaching out to your bank.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
